        <item>
          <title>Australian who falsely claimed to have invented bitcoin is found in contempt of UK court</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LONDON (AP) — An Australian computer scientist who falsely claimed to be the founder of the bitcoin cryptocurrency was found Thursday to be in contempt of an order of London's High Court and was sentenced to 12 months in prison, suspended for two years.]]></description>
